label chapter_1_part_3_2_jess:
    show jess neutral at center
    with dissolve

    "Jessica was the first to sit down as she was still carrying the boy in her arms."

    show mari neutral at right
    with dissolve

    mari "Do you mind if I sit next to you?"

    jess "Not at all. In fact, I really do need some sister company every once in a while."

    "Maria then sat next to her, their bellies touching each other."

    jess "Hmm... I love feeling our bellies touching..."

    mari "So do I... It makes our babies interact with each other..."

    show dijo neutral at left
    with dissolve

    dijo "Geez, you two... I know you are sisters, but you make it sound like you're married."

    mari  "Sorry..."
    jess "Sorry..."

    dijo "It's alright... I'll go to sleep."

    hide dijo neutral with dissolve

    "And so, Dijonay and the others went to sleep in their tents, leaving both Maria and Jessica with the boy."

    hide jess neutral
    hide mari neutral
    with dissolve

    jump chapter_1_part_3_3